dct_description_sm: This flat map, prepared in November 2018 by Data You Can Use, presents the percent of registered votes who cast a ballot in the 2016 Presidential election by voter ward for the City of Milwaukee. The data is sourced from the City of Milwaukee Election Commission. For more information, please visit Data You Can Use.
